%h3{style: "border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5; color: #434950; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 30px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px;" }
  Hi
  #{@registration.first_name},

.content
  .left.inline{ style: "width: 100%; min-width: 260px; display: inline-block;" }
    %p.lead{ style: "font-size: 18px; color: #333333; padding-bottom: 10px; line-height: 22px;"}
      We're delighted to offer you a place at our #{@event.title if @event.title.present?} workshop at #{@event.host.name} offices - #{@event.host.address_line_1}, #{@event.host.address_city}, #{@event.host.address_postcode}:
    .title{ style: "border-left: 4px solid #E5E5E5; font-size: 26.5px; margin: 0px 0 11px 0; padding: 0 10px;" }= @event.dates
    =link_to "View details", event_url(@event), style: "color: #E0330C; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px dotted #E0330C; "

    %div{style: "background-color: #F7F7F7; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 1px 1px 0 rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.5) inset, -1px -1px 2px rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.1) inset; font-size: 18px; padding: 12px 19px; text-align: center; margin: 31px 0 25px; border: 1px solid #dddddd;"}
      =link_to "Confirm your attendance status", invitation_url(@invitation), style: "color: #eb5d42; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)"

    %p.lead{ style: "font-size: 16px; color: #4E5563; padding-bottom: 10px; line-height: 22px;"}
      During the free 1.5-day workshop we'll explore the exciting world of Ruby on Rails, and build an application together.
      In order to secure your place, we ask you to confirm your attendance.
      We require this so we can re-allocate your place if you are unable to attend and give as many people as possible the opportunity to join us.

  .left.inline{ style: "width: 100%; min-width: 260px; display: inline-block;" }

    %h3{style: "color: #333333;"} What you need to bring?
    %p.lead{ style: "font-size: 16px; color: #4E5563; padding-bottom: 10px; line-height: 22px;"}
      Please
      %b bring your laptop and ID that will show a proof of your age
      with you
      %b (if you are under 18, you must be accompanied by an adult)!
      You should also try to pre-install Rails with instructions from:
      %br
      %br
      =link_to " http://guides.railsgirls.com/install", 'http://guides.railsgirls.com/install', style: "color: #E0330C; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px dotted #E0330C; "

    %h3{style: "color: #333333;"} What happens next?

    %p.lead{ style: "font-size: 16px; color: #4E5563; padding-bottom: 10px; line-height: 22px;"}
      We start off on
      %span{style: "font-weight: 500;"}on #{@event.starts_on.strftime("%A")} the #{@event.starts_on.day.ordinalize } of #{@event.starts_on.strftime("%B")}, with our Installation Party at 6:30pm.
      The goal of the evening is to get you set up for the saturday workshop. We will provide dinner and drinks.
      %br
    %p.lead{ style: "font-size: 16px; color: #4E5563; padding-bottom: 10px; line-height: 22px;"}
      On
      %b #{@event.ends_on.strftime("%A")}
      weâ€™ll dive into development. Our day will start at
      %b{style: "font-weight: 500;"} 9am with breakfast and introduction.
      We will then split into small groups of 3 people (2 students + 1 coach) to work on the tutorials.
      There will be a break for lunch at 12:30 and for several lightning talks at 13:45.
      We will wrap up the workshop at around 5:30pm and enjoy the After Party from there on.

  .right.inline{ style: "width: 100%; min-width: 180px; margin-top: 25px; display: inline-block;" }
    =image_tag attachments['london-girl.png'].url, width: '180px'
    %div{style: "margin: 15px 0; "}
      %highlight{ style: "color: #333333; text-align: center; font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px" }Get excited and learn to build the web!
    %p.lead{ style: "font-size: 15px; color: #4E5563; margin-top: 25px;" }
      %strong Thank you
      for applying to our Rails Girls London workshop!

  = render 'sponsor/email_logos'
